    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Classifier<PERSON,FACE>, ReadableBinary, ReadWriteableBinary, WriteableBinary, Annotator<FACE,PERSON>, RestrictedAnnotator<FACE,PERSON>, IncrementalTrainer<Annotated<FACE,PERSON>>

    public class AnnotatorFaceRecogniser<FACE extends DetectedFace,PERSON>
extends FaceRecogniser<FACE,PERSON>
    A FaceRecogniser built on top of an IncrementalAnnotator. This class essentially adapts standard IncrementalAnnotator to work in the face recognition scenario.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
